## 📁 Project Structure

```
stable-diffusion-webui/
├── webui.py                  # Main application entry point
├── launch.py                 # Dependency installer & launcher
├── webui-user.bat / .sh      # ← Your personal config lives here
├── modules/                  # Core application logic
│   ├── api/                  # FastAPI REST endpoints
│   ├── cmd_args.py           # All available command-line flags
│   └── shared_options.py     # Runtime settings definitions
├── extensions-builtin/       # Bundled extensions (LoRA, ScuNET, SwinIR…)
├── extensions/               # User-installed extensions (auto-created)
├── models/                   # Model checkpoints, VAEs, LoRAs, upscalers
│   ├── Stable-diffusion/     # Place .safetensors / .ckpt files here
│   ├── Lora/                 # LoRA adapter files
│   └── VAE/                  # VAE files
├── embeddings/               # Textual Inversion embeddings
├── outputs/                  # Generated images are saved here
└── configs/                  # Model architecture YAML configs
```

