## 🔌 Adding Models

1. Download a `.safetensors` or `.ckpt` model from [Hugging Face](https://huggingface.co/models?pipeline_tag=text-to-image) or [Civitai](https://civitai.com)
2. Place it in `models/Stable-diffusion/`
3. Click the 🔄 **Refresh** button next to the checkpoint dropdown in the UI (no restart needed)

> ✅ **Prefer `.safetensors` format** — it's faster to load and protects against malicious pickle exploits.

