## 🛠️ Troubleshooting

| Problem | Solution |
|---------|----------|
| Black or green images | Add `--no-half` or `--no-half-vae` to your launch flags |
| CUDA out of memory | Use `--medvram` (4–6 GB) or `--lowvram` (2–3 GB) |
| Slow generation on NVIDIA | Install xFormers: add `--xformers` to launch flags |
| "No module named torch" | Delete the `venv/` folder and re-run the launch script |
| Port 7860 already in use | Add `--port 7861` (or any free port) to your launch flags |
| Corrupted model download | Delete the partial file from `models/` and restart |

